HOUSE BILL 1267
L6 6lr2367
By: Delegates Lehman, Pena–Melnyk, Barnes, Bartlett, Boafo, Chang, Holmes,
Rogers, and Taylor
Introduced and read first time: February 12, 2026
Assigned to: Economic Matters and Environment and Transportation
A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Patuxent Research Refuge and Beltsville Agricultural Research Center – Zoning
3 Classification
4 (Protecting Patuxent Research Refuge Act)
5 FOR the purpose of requiring a certain local zoning authority to designate and maintain
6 certain property in a zoning classification that restricts the uses in a certain manner
7 under certain circumstances; requiring the appropriate authority to maintain
8 certain property in a certain zoning classification that restricts the uses in a certain
9 manner under certain circumstances; and generally relating to land use.
10 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
11 Article – Land Use
12 Section 1–401(a)
13 Annotated Code of Maryland
14 (2012 Volume and 2025 Supplement)
15 BY adding to
16 Article – Land Use
17 Section 1–401(b)(19), 4–217, and 25–211
18 Annotated Code of Maryland
19 (2012 Volume and 2025 Supplement)
20 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
21 Article – Land Use
22 Section 1–401(b)(19) through (32)
23 Annotated Code of Maryland
24 (2012 Volume and 2025 Supplement)
25 BY repealing
26 Article – Land Use
